(Translated by Google) One of the most frequently eaten Brazilian breakfast restaurants Somerville is one of the most Brazilian restaurants in the Boston area This snack bar is always full of takeout/inside crowds Reasonable price and authentic taste There are all kinds of Brazilian snacks There are also super hearty burgers with very high cp value Fresh fruit smoothies and juices  ▪️Sanduíches Brazilian sandwich (hamburger) ♥♥♥♥♥ There are everything in it, just like the luxurious and enlarged version of the breakfast shop burger. All burgers have ham/cheese/lettuce/tomato/corn/small fries/mayonnaise, plus different meats and eggs, the most common order It is X-Tudo, the concept of a total sandwich, with bacon/drumsticks/eggs added, one can eat two meals (or one for two people), super recommended!!  Sanduíches’ menus almost always start with X-, X-Bacon / X-Burger / X-Salada / X-Fominha / X-File / X-Guloso... Friends said that X- stands for Cheese.  ▪️ The translation of Pastel seems to be Brazilian fried dumplings. The Pastel I have eaten are all oversized and rectangular, a bit like a pie. The outside is fried and crispy, and there are various flavors inside, such as cheese flavor, ground beef, ground chicken, cheese Chicken, corn, bacon, shrimp, etc. Brazilian friends will add "a lot" of tomato sauce and mayonnaise, and add one bite to one bite (it's really delicious!)  ▪️A dozen flavors of fresh smoothies/juices Most Brazilian snack bars offer fresh smoothies Some also have açaí smoothies Coconut flavor is also a very common smoothie  (Original) 最常吃的巴西早餐店之一 Somerville是波士頓地區最多巴西餐廳的區域之一 這家小吃店永遠都是滿滿的外帶/內用人潮 價位合理、口味地道 有各式各樣的巴西小吃 還有cp值非常高的超豐盛漢堡 新鮮現打水果冰沙和果汁  ▪️Sanduíches 巴西三明治(漢堡) ♥♥♥♥♥ 裡什麼都有, 就像是早餐店漢堡的豪華加大版, 所有的漢堡都有 火腿/起司/生菜/番茄/玉米/小薯條/美乃滋，加上不同肉和蛋, 最常點的是X-Tudo, 總匯三明治的概念, 裡面加了培根/雞腿排/蛋, 一份可以吃兩餐 (或兩個人吃一個), 超級推薦!!  Sanduíches 的菜單幾乎都是 X- 開頭, X-Bacon / X-Burger / X-Salada / X-Fominha / X-File / X-Guloso…  友人表示 X-代表 起司Cheese 的意思  ▪️ Pastel 翻譯似乎是巴西炸餃，我所吃過的 Pastel都是超大一個長方形，有點像餡餅，外面炸的酥脆，裡面會有各種不同口味，起司口味、碎牛肉、碎雞肉、起司雞肉、玉米培根、蝦等等，巴西友人都會加上 “大量” 的番茄醬和美乃滋，吃一口加一次 (加了真的很好吃 !)  ▪️十幾種口味的現打冰沙/果汁 大部分巴西小吃店都有提供現打冰沙 有的還會有巴西莓açaí 冰沙 椰子🥥口味也是很常點的冰沙

This place is receiving 5 stars specifically because they sell and make on site this special "Sugar Water" which they grind from actual raw sugar cane right in front of your eyes. This is no normal sugar water, do not expect Kool-Aid. This is an earthy/grassy sweet beverage that I tried in Central America a few years back and figured it was a local delicacy. I was so happy to find this place and that they produce such a unique beverage locally. I will be back to try their sandwiches and pastries.

I came here because I read about how cheap their sandwiches are. The prices have gone up slightly, but they give you a massive sandwich, still a great deal for the price (starting from $5)! It's a hole-in-the-wall bakery and the menu is mostly still in Portuguese and they also have feijoadas on the weekends. Their fillings are at first glance pretty standard, but most of the sandwiches are also stuffed with corn and fried potato sticks!
